Name: Zeta Complex
About the game: Zeta Complex is a hardcore tactical platformer with roguelike elements that challenges your wit and reaction. Find your way through ever-changing labyrinths while not being killed by deadly turrets! A variety of weapons and utility abilities is to help you with that, but you'll have to be cunning and fast-minded to use them to full potential.
